title: New: UPSAHL – Can You Hear Me Now
body:
Powerful songwriting from Phoenix’s **UPSAHL** on her latest track, _Can You Hear Me Now_.

Heavily inspired by the likes of Feist and Regina Spektor, there’s a real sleekness to the composition here, as well as feeling perfect for summer playlists. Check it out below.
